    {
      "instruction": "<p>Add the <strong>sliced green chilli </strong>to a small bowl with the juice of <strong>half</strong> your <strong>lime[s]</strong> and a pinch of<strong> salt </strong>and<strong> sugar</strong></p><p>Give everything a good mix up and set aside to pickle – this is your <strong>quick-pickled chilli</strong></p><p>Combine your <strong>carrot & cabbage slaw mix</strong> in a large bowl with the juice of the <strong>remaining</strong> <strong>lime</strong>, the <strong>chopped</strong> <strong>coriander</strong> and a pinch of <strong>salt</strong> – this is your <strong>coriander slaw</strong></p>",
