      "instruction": "<p>Dissolve your <strong>chipotle</strong> <strong>paste</strong> (can't handle the heat? Go easy!), <strong>tomato</strong> <strong>paste</strong> and <strong>vegetable stock mix </strong>in 100ml <span class=\"text-purple\">[130ml]</span> <span class=\"text-danger\">[175ml] </span><strong>boiled water </strong>– this is your <strong>chipotle stock</strong></p>",
